msgid ""
"From the Mattermost distribution, upload the ``client`` directory to S3 "
"and rename it to ``static``. You can use the AWS CLI command below from "
"within the ``client`` directory  to upload all the files to S3. The files"
" must be publicly readable with the permission ``public-read``."
msgstr ""

